Introduction

Jaeyun is a Korean-New Zealander singer under MNH Entertainment. He made his official debut as a member of the boy group 8TURN on January 30th, 2023.

Prior to debut, he was best known for participating in the reality survival shows "BOYS24" and "MIXNINE."
